name: PornArtGen
description:
This is my first merge, so go easy on me.

This is my personal 30+ checkpoint merged swiss army of porn model. I wanted to combine the best aspects of Deliberate (amongst many others) with the poses of the better anime porn checkpoints. The end result is more facial variations than I see from any individual merge, and it favors my subject matter (it crushes at retro porn/ads/etc.). It does really well at SFW images if you negative "nudity," but your mileage may vary.
